    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729380/extras/cf4e546aaaa05bc3d60acec2be3d67ad.poster.avif?t=1668655066\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729380/extras/cf4e546aaaa05bc3d60acec2be3d67ad.webm?t=1668655066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729380/extras/cf4e546aaaa05bc3d60acec2be3d67ad.mp4?t=1668655066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NOTHING BUT A GLITCH</h2> Play as Guro, a bog-slogger set to free the world of shackles of the corporation by submerging herself into the deepest layers of the cyberspace and destroying the system from within. When the rules of the game are broken, all you need is a glitch.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INTO THE BOG</h2>Even with the Bog constantly changing, you are able to retain permanent shards of it. They grant you power to progress and design your next attempt instead of relying on the mercurial nature of the system. As you get farther into the network, you discover new ways of playing the game. Or breaking it.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HARD RESET</h2>TECHNOBOG is built for replayability. Not only do you get to choose between numerous options within a single run, you can also affect how the entire game is played by discovering new content. Your progress in one run opens up new levels for you to discover when you start the next one.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729380/extras/2d445c74e8932eb0e62167a88cb5f866.poster.avif?t=1668655066\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729380/extras/2d445c74e8932eb0e62167a88cb5f866.webm?t=1668655066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729380/extras/2d445c74e8932eb0e62167a88cb5f866.mp4?t=1668655066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE SCENE</h2>You're not alone in your journey to the core of this system. Not completely. Make friends and enemies as you develop your relationship with others throughout numerous attempts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729380/extras/d5f0de64a6d4a0e45db6e727328c8c1f.poster.avif?t=1668655066\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729380/extras/d5f0de64a6d4a0e45db6e727328c8c1f.webm?t=1668655066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729380/extras/d5f0de64a6d4a0e45db6e727328c8c1f.mp4?t=1668655066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Aim your strike and slice any obstacle in your path in any way you desire<br></li><li> Transform into a beam of light<br></li><li> Grow a tentacle arm<br></li><li> Teleport onto your dagger<br></li><li> A unique blend of 3D platforming and hack and slash<br></li><li> Emphasis on creativity in combat<br></li><li> Made by one person</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE MANY LAYERS OF THE BOG</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729380/extras/d72156779659acda0e22e6fbf362680d.poster.avif?t=1668655066\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729380/extras/d72156779659acda0e22e6fbf362680d.webm?t=1668655066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729380/extras/d72156779659acda0e22e6fbf362680d.mp4?t=1668655066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Get ready to explore the TECHNOBOG with all its layers. From the sci-fi chambers inspired by the classics of the 80s to the colorful toxic grasslands.",
